"      Dormicum (AE, AR, AT, BB, BD, BE, BF, BG, BH, BJ, BM, BS, BZ, CH, CI, CO, CY, CZ, DE, DK, EC, EE, EG, ES, ET, FI, GH, GM, GN, GR, GY, HK, HR, HU, ID, IQ, IR, JM, JO, JP, KE, KP, KW, LB, LR, LU, LY, MA, ML, MR, MT, MU, MW, MX, NE, NG, NL, NO, OM, PH, PK, PL, PT, PY, QA, RU, SA, SC, SD, SE, SG, SK, SL, SN, SR, SY, TH, TN, TR, TT, TW, TZ, UG, UY, YE, ZM, ZW);",
